== 歷史 ==

阿開木的果實在1778年之前被運到了[[牙買加|牙買加]]。<ref name="jis">{{cite web| author=| year=| title=This is Jamaica| work=National Symbols of Jamaica| url=http://www.jis.gov.jm/special_sections/This%20Is%20Jamaica/symbols.html| accessdate=2006-06-04| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060619153047/http://www.jis.gov.jm/special_sections/This%20Is%20Jamaica/symbols.html| archivedate=2006-06-19| deadurl=no}}</ref>後來逐漸被做成了[[加勒比地區|加勒比地區]]的一道重要菜肴。

[[威廉·布萊|威廉·布萊]]船長在1793年將這種植物從[[牙買加|牙買加]]帶到了[[邱園|邱園]]。其常用名“ackee”來自非洲[[阿坎語|阿坎語]]。<ref name="language">{{cite book | first=Allan | last=Metcalf | authorlink= | coauthors= | year=1999 | title=The World in So Many Words | url=https://archive.org/details/worldinsomanywor00metc | edition= | publisher= | location= | isbn=0-395-95920-9 }}</ref>

== 種植和使用 ==

[[File:Ackee_and_Saltfish.jpg|thumb]]，一道牙買加傳統菜肴]]

儘管原産於非洲，不過最常用到阿開木果作為食物的國家卻是牙買加，它同時也是牙買加[[國樹|國樹]]，以阿開木做出的[[阿開木煮鹹魚|阿開木煮鹹魚]]也被譽為[[國菜|國菜]]。現在也有阿開木酒出現在牙買加。<ref name='National geographic'>http://travel.nationalgeographic.com/travel/top-10/national-food-dishes/ {{Wayback|url=http://travel.nationalgeographic.com/travel/top-10/national-food-dishes/ |date=20160927030252 }} National food dishes</ref><ref name='national dishes'>{{cite web |url=http://www.jis.gov.jm/special_sections/Independence/symbols.html |title=National Symbols |work=Emancipation & Independence |publisher=Jamaica Information Service |accessdate=2011-10-18 |archive-date=2011-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028013030/http://www.jis.gov.jm/special_sections/Independence/symbols.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

阿開木乾燥的種子、果實、樹皮和葉子都有藥用價值。<ref name='medicinal'>{{cite web|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|url=http://www.ethnobiomed.com/content/pdf/1746-4269-6-12.pdf|title=RESEARCH Open Access Uses, traditional management, perception of variation and preferences in ackee ( Blighia sapida K.D. Koenig) fruit traits in Benin: implications for domestication and conservation|work=|pages=|publisher=|accessdate=2013-06-25|curly=|archive-date=2014-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141127053303/http://www.ethnobiomed.com/content/pdf/1746-4269-6-12.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

因為有中毒風險，所以[[美國食品和藥物管理局|美國食品和藥物管理局]]一度禁止阿開木進口，不過後來禁令被取消了。<ref>{{cite web|last=|url=http://www.accessdata.fda.gov/cms_ia/importalert_64.html|title=Import Alert 21-11|work=|pages=|publisher=[[FDA|FDA]]|accessdate=2013-06-25|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506203233/https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/cms_ia/importalert_64.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 毒性機理 ==
[[File:Hypoglycin_A.svg|thumb]]

阿開木果實不能吃的部份和未成熟的果實是有毒的，含有[[次甘氨酸A|次甘氨酸A]]和{{le|次甘氨酸B|Hypoglycin B|B}}。次甘氨酸A在種子和[[子殼|子殼]]中都有發現，次甘氨酸B只存在於種子中。<ref name="features"/>在人體中，該物質會被轉化為{{link-en|甲叉环丙基乙酸|Methylene cyclopropyl acetic acid
}}（MCPA），後者會抑制包括[[酰基辅酶A|酰基辅酶A]]在內的數種[[酶|酶]]。次甘氨酸也會使[[輔酶A|輔酶A]]、[[肉鹼|肉鹼]]和[[肉碱棕榈酰转移酶|肉碱棕榈酰转移酶]]的<ref name="Clinical Significance of Carnitine Function">{{cite book | first= Parveen J.| last= Kumar | authorlink= | coauthors= | year=2006 | title= Clinical Medicine | edition= 5| publisher=Saunders (W.B.) Co Ltd | location= | isbn=978-0-7020-2579-2 }}</ref>生物利用率不可逆地下降，最終抑制[[脂肪酸|脂肪酸]]的[[β-氧化|β-氧化]]。<ref name="Clinical">{{cite book | first= Vishwanath | last= SarDesai | title=Introduction to Clinical Nutrition | url= https://archive.org/details/introductiontocl0000sard | publisher=Marcel Dekker Inc. | location=New York | year=2003 | isbn=0-8247-4093-9}}</ref>臨床上這種中毒現象被叫做[[牙买加呕吐病|牙买加呕吐病]]。<ref>[http://www.scq.ubc.ca/the-ackee-fruit-blighia-sapida-and-its-associated-toxic-effects/ THE ACKEE FRUIT (BLIGHIA SAPIDA) AND ITS ASSOCIATED TOXIC EFFECTS] {{Wayback|url=http://www.scq.ubc.ca/the-ackee-fruit-blighia-sapida-and-its-associated-toxic-effects/ |date=20210310061908 }}, The Science Creative Quarterly</ref>

